{{Latin place names}} Users of [[New Latin language|Neo-Latin]] have taken the Latin language to places the [[Rome|Romans]] never went; hence a need arose to make '''Latin names of mountains''' that did not exist when Latin was a living language.
==Strategies for constructing Latin names== {{see also|Latin names of cities#Strategies for constructing Latin names}}
