{{Orphan|date=October 2015}}
In [[contracts]], [[research and development]], research administration, and [[project management]], '''milestone fees''' are fees for the development of a [[deliverable]] to be completed under the applicable [[statement of work]]. Milestone fees do not include [[sales tax]] or any other [[taxes]].
